RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

98-1974. State ex rel. Sysco Food Serv. of Cleveland, Inc. v. Indus. Comm.

In Mandamus. Reported at 89 Ohio St.3d 612, 734 N.E.2d 361. On motion for reconsideration and on amicus curiae motion for leave to file under S.Ct.Prac.R. XI by the Ohio Self-Insurers’ Association. *1453Motions denied.

Douglas, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., dissent.
